3.3717, 147.6016, 147.8571, 148.3584, 147.9063, 147.105, 148.297, 147.4665, 145.3361, 145.939, 146.7354, 146.34, 146.6739, 147.3001, 148.2162, 149.3785, 149.8724, 150.7815, 149.6675, 150.6825, 150.4537, 150.6358, 149.3953, 150.3964, 150.9062, 149.6469, 150.8267, 149.3998, 148.8885, 148.0477, 148.7824, 149.0008, 148.7246, 149.353, 151.2959, 150.4865, 150.7794, 151.8784, 152.1104, 150.4503, 150.9498, 151.6524, 152.9082, 152.7541, 152.7307, 152.5546, 152.6106, 152.7809, 151.2374, 150.9198, 150.8399, 151.5644, 151.7509, 151.5596, 152.3667, 150.9525, 151.5561, 151.8295, 152.0433, 152.1658, 150.8739, 150.6021, 151.0079, 151.9451, 152.4006, 150.8865, 150.5276, 150.3588, 150.904, 150.7992, 151.031, 149.706, 148.3596, 147.4832, 148.755, 148.7331, 148.4985, 149.4918, 148.438, 147.2344, 146.8388, 146.5966, 145.3517, 145.8933, 145.5463, 146.2202, 144.4263, 143.9264, 142.9691, 142.3805, 141.1843, 142.1829, 141.8789, 142.7344, 143.3108, 142.3146, 140.7192, 141.1442, 140.0821, 138.7851, 139.7325, 140.0583, 140.3282, 140.9987, 143.5937, 142.8856, 138.7628, 139.3581, 141.1885, 141.8477, 141.9272, 144.0346, 145.118, 148.7478, 146.9044, 146.6933, 143.4145, 140.8759, 140.9297, 142.0656, 136.2875, 137.1325, 137.6804, 137.2465, 139.5336, 138.0875, 137.6131, 138.4086, 141.509, 141.6493, 143.5707, 138.8266, 133.4033, 134.0637, 132.5455, 129.1304, 121.6642, 126.8795, 125.1979, 123.1906, 123.3734, 120.7192, 119.3916, 115.5379, 115.5691, 115.1176, 117.677, 117.461, 119.9903, 119.0372, null, null, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>换手率分布均匀度 UTD 因子 -- 通过</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>UTD (Uniformity of Turnover Distribution) 因子衡量品种日内成交量分布的均匀程度。核心思路是：日内成交越均匀的品种，未来表现越好。因子先计算每日分钟成交量的标准差（TurnVol_daily）衡量当日交易平稳性，再在 N 日回看期内计算 TurnVol_daily 的变异系数（CV = std/mean）。CV 越高说明日内成交波动性本身在时间序列上也不稳定，预示更差的未来表现。做多低 UTD（成交均匀的品种），做空高 UTD（成交不均匀的品种）。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.42</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>2.3%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>5.4%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-13.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3432</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.74</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-1.05</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.33 / 1.08</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.42</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.95</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.16</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.27</span></td><td>1.91</td><td>1.98</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.06</span></td><td>0.21</td><td>1.92</td><td>1.55</td><td>-0.0</td><td>0.03</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.16</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.1</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>volume</code></td><td>成交量</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 分钟级（聚合到日频输出）</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 20 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 20 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3921</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>89.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>33.3</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{TurnVol}_{\\text{daily},t} = \\text{std}(\\text{volume}_{t,1}, \\text{volume}_{t,2}, \\ldots, \\text{volume}_{t,M})</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">M</span> 为当日有效分钟 bar 数（要求 <span class=\"math-tex\">M \\geq 60</span>）。</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{UTD}_{t} = \\frac{\\text{std}(\\text{TurnVol}_{\\text{daily},t-N+1}, \\ldots, \\text{TurnVol}_{\\text{daily},t})}{\\text{mean}(\\text{TurnVol}_{\\text{daily},t-N+1}, \\ldots, \\text{TurnVol}_{\\text{daily},t})}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">N</span> 为回看天数（最优参数 <span class=\"math-tex\">N=40</span>）。</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_{i,t} = f(\\text{rank}(-\\text{UTD}_{i,t}))</div>\n<p>低 UTD 排名高 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\to</span> 做多，高 UTD 排名低 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\to</span> 做空。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.485, vol_target_scale 导致年化波动 0.62(远超0.15目标), 分钟聚合close不连续致rvol异常</td><td>基础UTD因子实现, lookback=20/40/60, hold=lookback</td><td>utd_60_raw 0.485</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>缩短 hold_days(5/10) 导致换手率从 0.25 跳到 0.80, 费用吞噬收益</td><td>增加参数网格, 添加IC gate</td><td>Sharpe下降到0.42(回归)</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td><strong>关键转折</strong>: 移除 vol_target_scale, 改用 rank_to_continuous/rank_to_ls 直接做仓位, 保持 hold=20</td><td>不做波动率缩放, 对比连续和离散信号</td><td>Sharpe跃升至0.76</td></tr><tr><td>R4</td><td>触发 cs+ts 归一化(R3&gt;0.5), 聚焦 lookback=40(R3最优), 增加 hold=30/40/60 降低换手</td><td>10个变体含 raw+cs+ts, 参数网格覆盖</td><td><strong>Sharpe 1.33, 全部 gate 通过</strong></td></tr></table></div>\n<p>关键转折点：R3 发现分钟数据聚合到日频后的 close 列不适合计算 realized vol（因为每日只有一个数据点，log return 的 rolling std 失真），移除 vol_target_scale 后 Sharpe 从 0.49 直接跃升到 0.76。R4 触发时序归一化 (_ts) 进一步提升至 1.33。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 分钟 K 线 (comm_data/1min/kline_all.parquet)</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全部 59 个商品期货品种</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 20 日再平衡（最优），30-60 日也有效</li>\n<li><strong>信号方向</strong>: 截面因子（做多成交均匀的品种，做空成交不均匀的品种）</li>\n<li><strong>夜盘处理</strong>: 过滤 21:00+ bars 防前视偏差</li>\n<li><strong>日期对齐</strong>: SHIFT_FIX 信号 T 日 -&gt; 仓位 T+1 日生效</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 因子基于分钟成交量分布，依赖分钟数据质量；时序归一化 (_ts) 提升最大，说明因子在不同品种的绝对水平差异大，需标准化</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 38.33s</li>\n</ul>"}